&quot;Oh, good, your still here.  While your out, can you pick up this stuff?&quot;  He took the offered pad and looked it over.<br>
&quot;Sure.&quot;  The things were pretty simple, light bulbs, toilet paper, bread, milk, cheese, coffee, tea, the basics.  They needed nothing else.  &quot;We'll be back soon.&quot;  <br>
